channel.title: Info why I made the Report List, NO WANABE MOD!
channel.description:
Ok some people keep Saying/Pming to me Wanabemod noob, Cause of that Report List.
Im doing this because. Im august my account has been Reset. It was over spammed and I think that was the problem, had too many messages, the acc was already lagging etc. Day later it was reset but I dont think the Admins did that without saying it to me. Now i made the Mass Report list because I want to get Rid of the Spam.
[b]Just for the People who dont know what I mean:[/b] Im scared to get reset again cause of the Spam etc. Just remember that.
Most people already know this. So stop saying im just Doing that list cause of Wanabemod. It will be a dream to become a mod but I would never be one I think. Everyone has like 5% chance or something? Or 2%? lol
Whatever just say this again. Dont call this spam because some ppl need to know this.
